data.description: LAKEFRONT POOL HOME has everything you are looking for in South Fort Myers/Estero area. Sliding glass doors welcome you to the outdoor oasis & immediate water views! Sparkling, heated pool has raised spa with waterfall that overlooks the firepit gathering area. The screened lanai & expansive, pavered pool area is great for entertaining. 4+ bedrooms, 2 ½ baths & 2 separate living/family rooms (one would be a great home office or craft room). 1st flr Owner's retreat offers dual vanities/sinks, sep shower, walk in closet & seating area. Kitchen is updated with newer appliances, island, raised bar & pantry cabinet. Formal dining room along with casual eating spot. Upstairs offers a large bonus room great for guests or teens to have their own space. Newer: roof (2023), pool heater, screened front porch, electric panel for portable generator. Updated flooring is beautiful & easy to maintain.  Walking distance to the amenity center included in your LOW HOA fees ($130 a month!): Community pool, tennis, fitness, basketball, playground & sports courts! Local soccer & tennis fields, school nearby. Beautiful tree-lined boulevard with sidewalks, dog friendly.  Situated in South Fort Myers right next to Estero offering you convenience to schools, parks, shopping, International airport, FGCU, Gulf Coast Town Center & more.
